Coinapult Bitcoin extension
===========================

Installation instructions:

1. Upload the contents of this directory to the corresponding directories
   in your store. Usually, this module is distributed as an archive, which
   can simply be extracted in the base directory of Magento.

2. Visit https://coinapult.com/ (free signup required), and create API keys.

3. Navigate to System->Configuration, then Payment Methods, in the right menu.
   Open the Bitcoin tab and enter your Coinapult API Key and Secret.
   You may need to clear the store cache before Coinapult shows up.

4. Make sure "Enabled" is "Yes", and save.

Enjoy!

